sun.awt.X11.XException: Cannot write XdndAware property
    => http://bugs.sun.com/view_bug.do?bug_id=7027598
    => bug op Linux systemen voor jdk boven versie 1.6.0_22
    => fix:
        zet droptarget van JTextFields op null: <JTextField>.setDropTarget(null);
        http://bugs.sun.com/bugdatabase/view_bug.do?bug_id=7027598:
            "Workaround: Seems that adding components after invoking pack() causes the exception. Removing the first pack() solves it."            

